11
00:00:47,200 --> 00:00:48,520
I didn't see anything.

12
00:00:49,400 --> 00:00:50,000
All right.

13
00:00:50,240 --> 00:00:51,440
If you remember anything,

14
00:00:51,440 --> 00:00:53,770
