15
00:01:13,920 --> 00:01:14,580
Brother Hu.

16
00:01:15,240 --> 00:01:16,440
Coming, Captain Lin.

17
00:01:16,440 --> 00:01:17,240
Half a pound of pork belly.

18
00:01:17,240 --> 00:01:18,280
Sure, how are you cooking it?

19
00:01:18,280 --> 00:01:19,039
Chop it finely.

20
00:01:19,039 --> 00:01:20,600
Yinuo likes meatballs.

21
00:01:20,720 --> 00:01:21,400
Okay.

22
00:01:21,400 --> 00:01:23,320
High-end resorts and theme parks

23
00:01:23,320 --> 00:01:26,320
