24
00:01:27,240 --> 00:01:30,840
Beautiful scenery, outstanding talents, and thriving industries.

25
00:01:30,840 --> 00:01:34,039
With its unique charm and economic ecology, Donghai

26
00:01:34,039 --> 00:01:38,200
